(5, 5, '<!-- home !-->\n<div id="body-bottom">\n    \n    <div id="bottom-a" ><h3>About Lou Ryan</h3><br><img src="../images/lou-ryan_sm.jpg" class="floatLeft" ></img>Lou Ryan is a pioneer in combining traditional scientific principals with cognitive behavioral theories into structured lifestyle trainings.</div>\n        <div id="bottom-b"><h3>Achieve Your Goals!</h3><br><img src="../images/get-your-body.jpg" class="floatRight"></img>You have the ability, now choose your program and get started!</div>\n        <div id="bottom-c"><h3>How It Works</h3><br>SelfHelpWorks program offer its participants effective, successful lifestyle management and freedom from their emotionally-driven dependencies. Each of the programs is private and entirely confidential as well as personalized and interactive. Participants will watch a series of informational training videos.</div>\n    \n    <div class="clear"></div>\n</div>'),
